title: training never starts
body:
### Is there an existing issue for this?

- [X] I have searched the existing issues

### Bug description

when trying to train a network, almost any network (dlcrnet cannot even be created).
everything runs until the "starting training..." message, but nothing ever happnes, even a week after the command.

### Operating System

operating system - win10

### DeepLabCut version

deeplabcut.__version__
'2.2rc3'

 tensorflow.__version__
'2.5.0'


### DeepLabCut mode

single animal

### Device type

GPU: RTX 3090
CPU: Intel(R) Xeon(R) Gold 5122 CPU @ 3.60GHz   3.59 GHz  (2 processors)

### Steps To Reproduce

in DEEPLABCUT (installed using pip) or in DLC2107 (installed using the conda environment from github)
2. either run deeplabcut from gui or by command line:
